'''''Beroya''''' (meaning "[[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]]" in [[Mando'a/Legends|Mando'a]]) was a [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]]-designed and built [[Gladiator-class assault fighter|''Gladiator''-class assault fighter]] that was flown by [[Goran Beviin]].

==History==
Beviin used it during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]] and the [[Second Galactic Civil War]]. He took the ship to [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] during [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett's]] plan to break the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] blockade and get onto the [[Planet/Legends|planet]].

